OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,6,Fsome bright or sunny intervals. There
OL,7,Fwill be a scattering of showers, these
OL,8,Fmainly in the west. Showers dying out
OL,9,Flater.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers dying out this
OL,12,Fevening otherwise dry. The rest of the
OL,13,Fnight will be cloudy with occasional
OL,14,Frain spreading from the southwest.
OL,15,FFreshening wind along the east coast.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FRain spreading northeast for a
OL,18,Ftime in the morning. The afternoon
OL,19,Fwill be brighter with a few showers.
OL,20,FBrisk southwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
