OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,6,Fcloudy on Saturday and Sunday with a
OL,7,Ffew showers, some dry and brighter
OL,8,Fweather too. Chance of further showery
OL,9,Frain on Monday.
